name: Van Fest!- A Van Wizards Vibe
name_original: Van Fest!- A Van Wizards Vibe
description:
Van Fest is here!

A once a year event where vans from across the roads gather in one place to meet up, eat, and enjoy themselves to the most magical extent! 

This is an idea of things to incorporate into your van fest and why it's important to the Van Wizard's of the World!
